rows.label: qst300107_msg002
rows.name:
Those beasts consider Mokmo Onion
a delicacy. They can smell it a mile off
and come swarming.

rows.label: qst300107_msg003
qst300107_msg004
rows.name:
But Vandham always used to take
them out so casually, I don't know
how to tell which one the leader is!

rows.label: qst300107_msg005
rows.name:
We'll just have to take out the lot
of 'em, one by one!
